name: FNF B-side Psych Engine Port
description:
The porting Fanmade of the mod B-side of Friday Nigth funkin ' :D

The six weeks of mod b sides remixes now ported in psych engine!

Enjoy this great mod in one of the most popular and comfortable engines of all FNF (Own opinion)

And next to that enjoy the great sprites / animations made by the talented @Pump .... Animator ?, inspired by FNF Reanimated

Link to your channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYJ_g0H2VaP6NbRs3mvIvEQ

* If you are from B-side team and you do not agree with this project, please contact me, to delete or hide the project *
